HEADWORD: Heaver
<hw>Heav"er</hw> <pr>(h⟦emac⟧v"⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>One who, or that which, heaves or lifts; a laborer employed on
